{"tid":1785845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殺警實錄】警員車內遭轟10槍行刑式殺害 美警公開閉路電視片段","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T17:00:56.000Z","uid":210140,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2605b72831dd1b2c407f28f3cb3c7e7b1fc418d","tid":1785845,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"美國阿肯色州一名35歲警員卡爾（Stephen Carr）月初在警車內遭連轟10槍殺害，華盛頓縣警局周五公佈案件的調查進展，並公開閉路電視片段，可以見到卡爾被殺害的經過。<br />\n<br />\n事發在本月7日，卡爾當時身處一輛警車之中，警車泊在警署後面的停車場。片段所見，犯人菲利普斯（Landon T. Phillips）從後靠近警車，然後向卡爾開槍。警方稱卡爾的頭部被連轟10槍，當場死亡。警署內的警員聽到槍聲後立即趕到現場並追捕槍手，菲利普斯與警方駁火後被擊斃，警方指他分別持有兩個裝滿50發子彈及32發子彈的彈盒。<br />\n<br />\n警方在聲明提到，從菲利普斯的社交網賬戶所見，他對反執法機構的組織感到興趣，可能與他的行兇動機有關。華盛頓縣警局在Facebook發文寫道：「基於案情性質令人髮指及震驚，我們猶豫應否公開這些片段。但為了讓公眾了解當晚事件經過，我們決定公開片段。我們最先考慮到卡爾家人的感受，所以我們先讓他們看了片段然後才公開。」<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191216/60379625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F60379625&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7lRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=aad5f0af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F60379625&h=0fbaa84a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191216/60379625</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f7e0a824476e12e3d13568b0128b247b801b8b","tid":1785845,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"你點對人人點對你"},{"pid":"5d6199d0b1015276c4708c222aef2a015f20119f","tid":1785845,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:47:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔係所謂港警<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560d86e843b2194d0b0b14ffa059d9be36c6d936","tid":1785845,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92cd46fe8b8803339e85e705ec0b62c5f342c60","tid":1785845,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"係美國一早<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09b70c3e7b15ecee4d4451204fe0569aa4ef644","tid":1785845,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:57:18.000Z","msg":"種下既因，終成果"},{"pid":"ba85ebc351aa6aa0bae055bdaf6e19bf007ebe2b","tid":1785845,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"香港市民有槍權嘅 班撚樣死咗十世"}]}